item.title: Put Off and Put On
item.description:
Pastor Mike Jonker shares how the church is made up of all kinds of people who all have their own stories and how Jesus wants us all to put off the things that aren't part of who we are in Jesus and put on the things that define us as believers and followers of Christ.

item.title: 2025 Yearly Themes
